<subSubSection lastPageId="35" lastPageNumber="36" pageId="34" pageNumber="35" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="34.[151,1436,1660,1979]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1918,1942]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="34" pageNumber="35" reason="1">Etymology.</emphasis>
Named after Jos Dils who collected the 
<typeStatus box="[792,890,1918,1942]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">holotype</typeStatus>
and all but two of the 
<typeStatus box="[1146,1253,1919,1943]" pageId="34" pageNumber="35">paratypes</typeStatus>
and contributed enormously to this revision by making his specimens freely available.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="35.[151,1436,1967,2021]" pageId="35" pageNumber="36">
